            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Small corrections (<2%) were made for traces of natural",
                "neodymium as determined from the amount of Nd-142",
                "present. Small corrections (<2%) were also applied for",
                "the thermal capture on Nd143 to form Nd144 and on Nd145",
                "to form Nd146. The calculated holdup of Ce144 was",
                "added to the Nd144 measured to provide the total chain",
                "yield for the mass 144 position."
              ]
